  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3025220/extras/e459320aa4c9367a6555e96274965fcd.poster.avif?t=1754190726\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3025220/extras/e459320aa4c9367a6555e96274965fcd.webm?t=1754190726\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3025220/extras/e459320aa4c9367a6555e96274965fcd.mp4?t=1754190726\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Game  Synopsis:</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In  the  distant  reaches  of  outer  space  lies  an  experimental  base  where  extraterrestrial  beings  convert  humans  into  animals  using  a  catalyst  to  satisfy  their  peculiar  needs.  Depending  on  the  catalyst  used,  the  transformed  animal  forms  vary.  Here,  you  are  a  human  who  has  escaped  from  the  laboratory,  evading  the  pursuit  of  enemies  while  utilizing  acquired  transformation  items  to  switch  between  human  and  animal  forms.  Explore  and  unravel  the  mysteries  of  the  game's  levels  by  leveraging  these  different  forms.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3025220/extras/159bb78846ed7719812322da60080f96.poster.avif?t=1754190726\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3025220/extras/159bb78846ed7719812322da60080f96.webm?t=1754190726\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3025220/extras/159bb78846ed7719812322da60080f96.mp4?t=1754190726\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3025220/extras/5a26f8d44a7e85c29d4257d8d98d2415.poster.avif?t=1754190726\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3025220/extras/5a26f8d44a7e85c29d4257d8d98d2415.webm?t=1754190726\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3025220/extras/5a26f8d44a7e85c29d4257d8d98d2415.mp4?t=1754190726\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3025220/extras/2017c74ed2071164dc8a3c401fffd073.poster.avif?t=1754190726\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3025220/extras/2017c74ed2071164dc8a3c401fffd073.webm?t=1754190726\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3025220/extras/2017c74ed2071164dc8a3c401fffd073.mp4?t=1754190726\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Game  Announcement:</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The  game  will  be  updated  periodically  or  have  certain  level  contents  revised.  We  welcome  any  feedback  and  reviews  you  may  have.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3025220/extras/e459320aa4c9367a6555e96274965fcd.poster.avif?t=1754190726\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3025220/extras/e459320aa4c9367a6555e96274965fcd.webm?t=1754190726\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3025220/extras/e459320aa4c9367a6555e96274965fcd.mp4?t=1754190726\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Game  Synopsis:</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In  the  distant  reaches  of  outer  space  lies  an  experimental  base  where  extraterrestrial  beings  convert  humans  into  animals  using  a  catalyst  to  satisfy  their  peculiar  needs.  Depending  on  the  catalyst  used,  the  transformed  animal  forms  vary.  Here,  you  are  a  human  who  has  escaped  from  the  laboratory,  evading  the  pursuit  of  enemies  while  utilizing  acquired  transformation  items  to  switch  between  human  and  animal  forms.  Explore  and  unravel  the  mysteries  of  the  game's  levels  by  leveraging  these  different  forms.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3025220/extras/159bb78846ed7719812322da60080f96.poster.avif?t=1754190726\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3025220/extras/159bb78846ed7719812322da60080f96.webm?t=1754190726\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3025220/extras/159bb78846ed7719812322da60080f96.mp4?t=1754190726\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragra